<br>
1k damage to the mage, depending on where he's at at that moment, might drop him into the 'mob frenzy' level, at which point, all mobs aggro on his pet will come beat him into oblivion, and wasting his effort.<br>
<br>
What if the Mage doesn't have 3k mana left?<br>
<br>
Stun would basically require the pet to be aggro on something already. Could not trigger, send attack, and get full use of the skill.<br>
<br>
As proposed, there would be enough negative side effects that no mage would use it in anything other than a gung ho, need to kill it dead fast setting (which wizards with MB aren't being limited to). I'm not sure I'd want to use it even if it had mega boosts, if the negative effects were that bad.<br>
<br>
My thoughts, anyways<br>
