<br>
I think the objection with regards to engagement losing some use is a bit trivial but as I said above the more serious negative side-affects were my own device and not really central to the idea.<br>
<br>
The point is that FB represents an opportunity to grant Mages a true super-AA skill that could make not only using pets on bossmobs desireable but outright powerful without changing the nature of the rest of the game experience.<br>
<br>
Make FB actually make pets significantly perform better on bosses, and make it cost a good chunk of mana. The numebrs are irrelevant - I just think an opportnity exists within this broken skill to being a lot fo raid dignity and pride to Magicians. <p><B><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26251">Hogfather</A></b><P>
